## üìù COMANDOS √öTILES

```bash
# Dev local (frontend)
cd packages/pulzio-landing
pnpm dev
# Abre: http://localhost:3000

# Build frontend
pnpm build
# Genera carpeta `out/` para Firebase Hosting

# Deploy frontend
firebase deploy --only hosting

# Deploy functions
cd packages/pulzio-landing/functions
npm install
npm run build
cd ..
firebase deploy --only functions

# Deploy todo
firebase deploy

# Ver logs de functions
firebase functions:log

# Ver signups en Firestore
# Firebase Console ‚Üí Firestore ‚Üí waitlist collection
# O usar Firebase CLI:
firebase firestore:get waitlist

# Emulador local (functions)
cd functions
npm run serve
# Abre: http://localhost:5001

# Verificar estado de deployment
firebase hosting:sites:list
firebase functions:list
```

